&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Locking adjustment knob prevents accidental setting changes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimizes space and piping due to the integration of the regulator and mist separator.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Various pressure range settings accommodate most applications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Series is suitable for air blower applications that require clean air.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High filtration (0.3&#xb5;m).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

